flowchart LR
    U[Upstream Systems] --> API[Ingestion API]
    API --> B[(Azure Blob Storage)]
    API --> Q[Service Bus Queue or Event Hub]

    Q --> A1[Worker Pool Instance 1]
    Q --> A2[Worker Pool Instance 2]
    Q --> A3[Worker Pool Instance N]

    A1 --> DI[Azure Document Intelligence]
    A2 --> DI
    A3 --> DI

    DI --> RS[(Results Database or Blob)]
    A1 --> DLQ[Dead-Letter Queue]
    A2 --> DLQ
    A3 --> DLQ

    Q --> MON[Queue Depth and Throughput Metrics]
    DLQ --> MON
    DI --> MON
